{"tid":2369431,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好因為間舖頭以前係黃店就沖去幫襯","createTime":"2021-01-17T06:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T07:11:14.000Z","uid":300420,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"94c07d1f39bc08c75ef8d3a68b7be75c2b71c6c4","tid":2369431,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n大家都知龍門冰室屯門店執柒咗<br />\n而家間鋪轉咗一間叫做熱點餐廳嘅嘢<br />\n裏面嘅裝修 門面 甚至餐具都同以前嘅龍門冰室一模一樣<br />\n但係食物質素真係完全唔撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我幫襯咗呢間熱點兩次<br />\n第一次我買咗個黑椒午餐肉雞扒飯<br />\n啲午餐肉梅嘅 塊雞扒仲薄過榮式雞排<br />\n汁又少 飯又乾<br />\n但係杯凍奶茶仲係以前龍門冰室嘅味道（我幾鍾意嗰隻奶茶） 所以決定俾多次機會佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我頭先落去幫襯咗第二次<br />\n嗌咗個燒汁龍利柳炸生蠔意粉配凍奶茶<br />\n杯凍奶茶就冇乜問題嘅 但係盒意粉就係咁樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaciTMm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaciTMm.png&h=00b53016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（我喺影相之前食咗啖意粉同咬咗塊魚柳一啖）<br />\n<br />\n都係一樣 汁好撚少 搞到啲意粉好乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n魚柳薄撚到我以為佢擺咗入液壓機壓兩下先比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炸蠔我一咬落去一陣強烈腥味出咗嚟 當然我都唔期望係咩優質蠔 但係嗰個真係唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰啲蠔底下嗰層三色豆仲係涷嘅 睇死佢係直接帶一大袋三色豆裏面挖出嚟直接鋪落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於盒意粉我剩係得四個字：<span class=\"red\">狗都唔食</span><br />\n<br />\n其實我對龍門嘅嘢食不嬲評價唔高（除咗佢啲奶茶） 會幫襯主要都係因為情懷<br />\n不過呢間野嘅嘢食係連龍門嘅水準都達唔到 純粹就係用龍門個殼吸客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw佢啲餐牌設計真係好柒 食埋今次之後都唔會再幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7d583e9fdc0c8da585464ce5a15168c0df649a","tid":2369431,"uid":367101,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"你比佢嗰個殻吸引仲好笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為你話黃變綠<br />\n屌你原來係裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fdefba8ca1f7bc7855751ff54d0a96f8fd6e634","tid":2369431,"uid":367101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的<br />\n大家都知龍門冰室屯門店執柒咗<br />\n而家間鋪轉咗一間叫做熱點餐廳嘅嘢<br />\n裏面嘅裝修 門面 甚至餐具都同以前嘅龍門冰室一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n不過呢間野嘅嘢食係連龍門嘅水準都達唔到 純粹就係用龍門個殼吸客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n寧願你話好奇去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你呢個理由真係鳩到不得了"},{"pid":"1d68f9f59964fd07bd758a93d8d85fc6942b7d4f","tid":2369431,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7d583e9fdc0c8da585464ce5a15168c0df649a","tid":2369431,"uid":367101,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"你比佢嗰個殻吸引仲好笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為你話黃變綠<br />\n屌你原來係裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"其實杯奶茶都有功勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我以後想飲嘅話可能會出去其他分店度飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417bb39750556210dc8d15914ab79ad4bde54294","tid":2369431,"uid":367101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d68f9f59964fd07bd758a93d8d85fc6942b7d4f","tid":2369431,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7d583e9fdc0c8da585464ce5a15168c0df649a","tid":2369431,"uid":367101,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"你比佢嗰個殻吸引仲好笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為你話黃變綠<br />\n屌你原來係裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"其實杯奶茶都有功勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我以後想飲嘅話可能會出去其他分店度飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"屯門d咖啡有間茶餐廳幾好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次帶你去試吓"},{"pid":"1281545628b07e632924d060a64f24821ba1ebc1","tid":2369431,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"417bb39750556210dc8d15914ab79ad4bde54294","tid":2369431,"uid":367101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d68f9f59964fd07bd758a93d8d85fc6942b7d